WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
We have some interesting results from our survey on hobbies.

00:05.000 --> 00:08.000
What's the most popular hobby?

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
Well, boys and girls have different hobbies.

00:12.000 --> 00:19.000
The girls like singing and dancing, but the boys like playing football and watching it.

00:19.000 --> 00:25.000
Oh, I see. Is there anything that both boys and girls like doing?

00:25.000 --> 00:30.000
Yes. Both boys and girls enjoy playing table tennis.

00:30.000 --> 00:33.000
Why is it good to have hobbies?

00:33.000 --> 00:37.000
You can learn about new things and develop new skills.

00:37.000 --> 00:43.000
For example, collecting stamps helps people learn about other countries

00:43.000 --> 00:47.000
and playing chess develops thinking skills.

00:47.000 --> 00:53.000
I see. My hobby is growing vegetables. Is that a popular hobby?

00:53.000 --> 00:58.000
Yes, it is. And your hobby helps the whole family.

